                </h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-forest/72 line-clamp-3">{guide.description}</p>
              </div>
              <span class="mt-5 text-xs font-bold text-leaf group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block">
                Read guide &rarr;
